(1, '<div align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Driver And Vehicle Details</span></strong><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">exact driver &amp; vehicle details will be shared with you at-least 2 hours prior to the journey.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">all drivers are trusted and verified by our team.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">any complaints related to driver should be reported to rashmi cabs within 2 days of the journey date.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Driver shall wait for 60 min. Post that booking will be cancelled with no refund.</span></li>\r\n</ul><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Pricing And Charges</span></strong><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">toll, parking , state tax , charges are to be paid by customer.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">fares includes driver allowances &amp; fuel charges only.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">any entrance / parking fee (if applicable) for all airport pickup and drop is to be paid by passenger directly to the driver.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">waiting charges not applicable upto 30 min,however it is recommended the passenger should reach boarding point 10 minutes early to the start time.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">km countng garage to garage. (max.10 km add) In case of extra kms, please pay directly to driver.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Waiting charges would be applicable after the cab reaches the boarding point, The first 15 minutes are free but post that the charge is 2 per minute and this amount has to be paid to the driver directly.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case of partial payment, the balance payment of trip needs to be paid in advance</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">at the time of pick-upYou need to collect the receipts from driver for any toll tax, state tax, night charges or extra km paid directly to the driver during the trip.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">RASHMI CABS is not liable to provide invoices for such amount.</span></li>\r\n</ul><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Pick &amp; Drop / Route</span></strong><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">for one-way booking,pickup would be done only from the scheduled pickup address and one drop is included multiple pickups / drops is not allowed.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">EXTRA PICK OR DROP WILL BE CHARGED EXTRA.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">pets and animals would not be allowed in the journey.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">the ac will be switched of during inclines and while climbing hilly areas.</span></li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Thanks for using our products and services (\"Services\"), </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The Services are provided by <strong>Rashmi Cabs.</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Located at Shop No 120, Madhav Hill Complex, Waghavadi Road, </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Bhavnagar, Gujrat, PIN - 364001</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Please read these terms carefully. By using our services, you are agreeing to all terms & conditions set forth. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In this agreement, the words \"including\" and \"include\" mean \"including, but not limited to</span></p><div align=\"justify\"><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">rashmicabs or rashmi is a technology company that makes available a platform for matchmaking  </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\"consumers\" seeking travel services from and to various destinations across gujrat with \"providers\"  </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">who can provide such travel services. The services are delivered </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">by the providers and rashmi cabs acts simply as marketplace platform.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Services  rashmi engages in the business of provision of </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">tour and travel related services through it\'s platform.Collectively these are referred to as Services.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Platform - rashmi engages in the business of provision of tour and travel related services </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">through its various platforms, including its website(s), communication systems like phone or SMS, </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">customer service & call centers, customer and vendor management systems, support ticketing systems and across its web and </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">mobile applications. Collectively, these ways of enabling our services are referred to as the rashmi Platform.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Consumer  An individual or organization that seeks services delivered by independent third-party Operators through the </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">rashmi\r\n Platform. Such an individual or organization is a customer on the \r\nrashmi Platform. A customer seeks services either for their </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">own use or use by another. However, a customer may or may not be the traveller (actual user of the service).</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Provider, Provider Partner or Third Party Provider  An individual or organization that operates </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">as an independent third-party and uses or interacts with the rashmi cabs platform to receive marketing leads </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">for consumers that can avail of the provider\'s service or product.A provider or Provider Partner is an independent third-party </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">who has a contractual relationship with rashmi.</span></li></ul><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">YOUR RASHMI ACCOUNT</span></strong><ul><li><span style