(4, '<div align=\"justify\"><div align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Driver And Vehicle Details</span></strong><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">exact driver &amp; vehicle details will be shared with you </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">at-least 2 hours prior to the journey.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">all drivers are trusted and verified by our team.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">any complaints related to driver should be </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">reported to rashmi cabs within 2 days of the journey date.</span></li>\r\n</ul><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Pricing And Charges</span></strong><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">toll, parking , state tax , charges are to be paid by customer.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">driver allowances RS 250/ DAY EXTRA.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">fares includes fuel charges only.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">any entrance / parking fee (if applicable) for </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">all airport pickup and drop is to be paid by passenger directly to the driver.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">waiting charges not applicable upto 30 min,however </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">it is recommended the passenger should reach boarding </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">point 10 minutes early to the start time.</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">km countng garage to garage. (max.10 km add),</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> In case of extra kms, please pay directly to driver.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">IF YOUR PICK UP OR DROP Between 11:59 PM to 5:59 AM, an additional night charge ( 500/night) will be applicable, </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">These charges to be paid directly to the driver.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Driver shall wait for 60 min. Post that booking will be cancelled with no refund, </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> In case of partial payment, the balance payment of trip needs to be paid in advance </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">at the time of pick-up You need to collect the receipts from driver </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">for any toll tax, state tax, night charges or extra km paid directly to the driver during the trip.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">RASHMI CABS is not liable to provide invoices for such amount.</span></li>\r\n</ul><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Pick &amp; Dop / Route</span></strong></div><ul>\r\n 	<li><div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">for one-way booking,pickup would be done only from </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">the scheduled pickup address and one drop is included </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">multiple pickups / drops is not allowed.</span></div></li>\r\n 	<li><div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">pets and animals would not be allowed in the journey.</span></div></li>\r\n 	<li><div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> the ac will be switched of during inclines and while climbing hilly areas.</span></div></li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Thanks for using our products and services (\"Services\"), </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The Services are provided by <strong>Rashmi Cabs.</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Located at Shop No 120, Madhav Hill Complex, Waghavadi Road, </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Bhavnagar, Gujrat, PIN - 364001</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Please read these terms carefully. By using our services, you are agreeing to all terms & conditions set forth. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In this agreement, the words \"including\" and \"include\" mean \"including, but not limited to</span><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">rashmicabs or rashmi is a technology company that makes available a platform for matchmaking  </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\"consumers\" seeking travel services from and to various destinations across gujrat with \"providers\"  </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; f