edentials or by calling us anytime on the 24x7 Customer Care Helpline +91 9974234111.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The advance amount is based on the trip estimated cost and will be adjusted against the final amount payable at the end of the trip.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case of vehicle accident/break-down the company will provide an alternate vehicle or will refund the\r\nadvance deposit if booking stands cancelled.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><b>Refunds are subject to Cancellation charges</b></span><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Rashmi Cabs doesn\'t take any guarantees of any kind while you book the cabs, and any material or immaterial\r\nloss due to usage of Rashmi Cabs cabs shall not be subject to any compensation.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case of no-show by the customer, or no intimation about change of time/date of booking, the booking advance amount will be fully forfeited. </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case the customer advance is less than 500 Rs, the company reserves the right to ask for more money to cover losses due to no show/cancellations.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case of a no-show by the driver for a scheduled departure, the company will provide an immediate replacement with a similar car and in case we can not find a replacement, a full refund of the advance amount will be done.</span></li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px none; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; color: #1d1d1d;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><b> </b></span></p>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><b>For booking modifications, following rules will apply</b></span><ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Remaining Payments after Advance or Payment at Trip Completion After paying advance amount, the remaining amount for the trip is always paid to the driver. </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">All modification requests should be communicated to us via a phone call to 9974234111 or a mail to care@RASHMIcabs.com and we will revert with response through email, Call or SMS.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">All payments done to the driver will be subject to adjustment against the final bill. Please call RASHMI Cabs at 9974234111 for any clarifications on billing or other things before/during/end of trip.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case, the final amount is less than the advance booking deposit (if any), RASHMI Cabs will refund the excess amount back to the customer  after confirming with the driver/operator. This refund is made within 5-7 working days after the completion of the trip.</span></li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px none; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; color: #1d1d1d;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><b>Refunds</b>\r\n</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">All refund requests are processed within 5-7 business days,  and payments are always done via the original source of payment for booking the cab. The refund requests done via Whatsapp and SMS are not taken into consideration.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In case of any issue regarding cancellation, please call our support team at 1800-102-8747.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ADVANCE NOT REFUNDABLE  IN ALL BOOKING FORMAT</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">RASHMI CABSwill not be held responsible for any cancellation or delay of service in case of any natural calamity, agitation or strike, traffic jam or road blockage, etc.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">RASHMI CABS reserves the right to cancel or change the booking of a vehicle at any point Any modifications/amendments to the booking are not allowed In the event of cancellation of a cab trip, We do not commit on particular fuel type vehicle like Petrol, Diesel or CNG. Cab will be provided on the basis of availability.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">If there is a No-Show from your end, i.e. you are not at the pickup location and/or your assigned Driver is unable to get in touch with you on your registered phone number on the scheduled pickup date and time, the Driver shall wait for a reasonable period of half an hour from the scheduled Booking time and thereafter may treat the Booking as cancelled with no refund.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>      ', 0, 5, '2018-12-11 07:37:42', 0, 5, '2018-12-11 07:37:42');
